text: Paracallia bonaldoi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 1998. It is known to be from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Paracallia bonaldoi. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Calliini Category:Beetles described in 1998
